Test Popout Windows   
    [Tags]    popout_windows
    
    ${pageTitle}=    Navigate To URL    ${LINK_NEW_WINDOWS}        
    Should Contain    ${pageTitle}   Open a New Browser Window
    
    Execute Javascript    window.scrollTo(0, 500)
    
    Click Element    ${NEW_WINDOW_BTN}    
    
